<h1 id="far-beam" sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="11">Far Beam</h1>

<p sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="13">The far beam component allows the user to visualise elements in the scene they can interact with from afar.</p>
<p sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="15">If you wish to customise the look of the beam, you can set the beam material by calling SetBeamMaterial with the material you wish to use. This material can have the following parameters if you wish to use them in your material.</p>
<ul sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="17">
<li sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="17"><strong sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="17">IsGrabbing</strong>: Scalar parameter. This value will be 0.0f if the user is not grabbing with the far cursor, 1.0f if they are.</li>
<li sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="18"><strong sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="18">handIndex</strong>: Scalar parameter. This value will be 0.0f for the left hand, 1.0f for the right hand.</li>
</ul>
<p sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="20">The default material for the far beam has the following parameters:</p>
<p sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="22"><img src="Images/FarBeamMatInterface.png" sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="22" alt="FarBeamMatInterface"></p>
<h2 id="far-beam-material-interface" sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="24">Far Beam Material Interface</h2>
<h3 id="base-color" sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="26">Base Color</h3>
<p sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="27">Color value for the solid beam</p>
<h3 id="emissive" sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="28">Emissive</h3>
<p sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="29">Emissive intensity for the solid beam</p>
<h3 id="gradation-hardness" sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="30">Gradation Hardness</h3>
<p sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="31">Scalar value to control the gradation hardness</p>
<h3 id="gradation-multiply" sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="32">Gradation Multiply</h3>
<p sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="33">Scalar value for the gradation of the solid beam</p>
<h3 id="gradation-offset" sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="34">Gradation Offset</h3>
<p sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="35">Scalar value for the gradation start position offset</p>
<h3 id="gradation-scale" sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="36">Gradation Scale</h3>
<p sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="37">Scalar value to control the gradation scale</p>
<h3 id="dotted-base-color" sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="38">Dotted Base Color</h3>
<p sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="39">Color value for the dotted beam</p>
<h3 id="linenumber" sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="40">LineNumber</h3>
<p sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="41">Scalar value to control the dot amount in the beam</p>
<h3 id="middlefade" sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="42">MiddleFade</h3>
<p sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="43">Scalar value to control the fade-out intensity of the dotted beam</p>
<h3 id="midfadeoffset" sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44">MidFadeOffset</h3>
<p sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="45">Scalar value to control the fade-out position of the dotted beam</p>
<h3 id="isgrabbing" sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="46">IsGrabbing</h3>
<p sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="47">System value for if the user is currently grabbing</p>
<h3 id="handindex" sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="48">handIndex</h3>
<p sourcefile="../../Docs/FarBeam.md" sourcestartlinenumber="49">System value used for distinguishing left from right hand</p>
